Microsoft Desktop Optimization Package (MDOP) je korisna grupa sledećih Windows alata:

-	App-V (App Virtualization); 
-	UE-V (User Experience Virtualization); 
-	MBAM (Microsoft BitLocker Administration and Monitoring); 
-	AGPM (Advanced Group Policy Management); 
-	DaRT (Diagnostics and Recovery toolset).

MDOP alati omogućavaju proaktivno upravljanje sa mogućim problemima u radu sa aplikacijama i sistemskim komponentama Windows 10 desktop računara.

MDOP je enterprise-ready, scalabilno, low-cost deployment rešenje, koje omogućava granularni error filtering, alerting, identifikaciju mogućih uzroka problema, daje predloge rešenja za otklanjanje problema čime Windows 10 desktop računari postaju mnogo stabilniji i pouzdaniji.

Setting up a errors and exceptions handling in a system is a big architectural challenge. 
If you want to listen and discuss about different kind of errors, affected groups of people, error categorization and error context this session is for you!
 
In this session we will cover:
- theory of errors;
- error and exception handling on architectural level;
- process mining over application log files;
